At least here she was defending herself from a man harrassing her

Dude this is why people say every person that doesn’t like CM movie or character is a man, misogynist etc, because these are their arguments and I hate it, also these kind of “arguments” are the ones with more support and visibility, I can talk for hours about what failed for me with this character/movie (well no, maybe minutes) but if you say THIS, everyone is so freaking right and you can’t find real reasons to hate/dislike her and you only do it  because she is a woman, they’re overreacting over this because they can’t find other reasons?

Sad
